<P>THE <HI>Right Education</HI> of CHILDREN RECOMMENDED, IN A SERMON, PREACHED IN A NEW SCHOOL-HOUSE IN NORTH-YARMOUTH, September 23, 1788; And now publi&s;hed by the De&s;ire of tho&s;e who heard it. <HI>By</HI> TRISTRAM GILMAN, A. M. PASTOR OF THE CHURCH IN THAT TOWN.</P>
