<P>To parents. Be exhorted, in every point, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">o your part, that your children may be well <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">cated. Afford them &s;uch in&s;tructions, as you <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">able, that are right and good. Set good ex|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">les before them, pray daily with and for them. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> the morning and evening &s;acrifice of family
